## Site Architecture

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `index.html` | **Production home page** (copy of `balerion-demo.html`) |
| `balerion-demo.html` | **Working draft** — edit this first, then sync to `index.html` |
| `ai-automation.html` | AI & Web Solutions service page (voice agents, website creation, sales, AI integration, workflow automation, custom agents) |
| `research.html` | Publications & Research — 15 cards from Google Scholar, filter pills, animated stats |
| `blog.html` | Blog listing page |
| `blog/*.html` | 5 individual blog posts |
| `frames/` | 145 WebP frames (frame_0001–frame_0145) for scroll-driven planet canvas animation |
| `ref/` | Reviewer profile images (zach.jfif, jeff.webp, ifran.jfif) |
| `brand_assets/` | Logo (Mir.png), brand guideline, reference designs |
| `serve.mjs` | Local dev server → `http://localhost:3000` |
| `screenshot.mjs` | Puppeteer screenshot utility |

## Critical Workflow
1. **Always edit `balerion-demo.html`** for home page changes
2. **Sync after edits**: `Copy-Item "balerion-demo.html" "index.html" -Force`
3. The title in `index.html` should be "Mir Md Tasnim Alam - Geospatial Data Scientist & AI Specialist"

## Design System

### CSS Variables (defined in `:root`)
- `--cosmic-black: #000000` — global background, MUST be pitch black
- `--cosmic-dark: #080808`
- `--cosmic-surface: #161616`
- `--accent-teal: #1E8289` — primary accent
- `--accent-gold: #DAA520` — secondary accent
- `--cosmic-blue: #1a3a5c`
- `--cosmic-purple: #2a1a4a`

### Typography
- Headings: `'Montserrat', sans-serif` — weight 700–900, letter-spacing `-0.02em` to `-0.04em`
- Body: `'Instrument Sans', sans-serif` — color `rgba(255,255,255,0.3)` to `0.5`
- Fonts loaded via Google Fonts CDN

### Shared Components (must be identical across all pages)
- **Logo**: Uses dotless `ı` (U+0131) with `.mir-i` and `.mir-dot` CSS classes
- **Navigation**: Fixed, transparent, with Home / About / Services / Blog links
- **"Get in Touch" button**: `.moving-border-btn` with animated `.glow-orb` SVG border
- **Footer**: Logo + `© 2026 Mir Md Tasnim Alam. All rights reserved.` + social links
- **Starfield**: `<canvas id="starfield">` with twinkling JS animation on all dark pages

### Card Styles
- **Service cards** (home): `.svc-card` — 4-column grid (`.svc-grid`), glassmorphic, radial gradient glow on hover
- **Blog cards** (home): `.blog-card-ft` — matching futuristic glassmorphic style
- **Glass cards** (ai-automation, research): `.glass-card` — `rgba(255,255,255,0.015)` bg, subtle border, hover lift

### Animation Libraries
- **GSAP + ScrollTrigger**: Planet scroll animation, text overlays, counter animations
- **Lenis**: Smooth scrolling
- **Intersection Observer**: `.scroll-reveal` / `.sr-d1` / `.sr-d2` staggered entrance animations

